            <head>
<title>The Adams Administration</title>
</head>
<div type="song">


<sp who="#burr"><speaker>BURR</speaker>
<l>How does Hamilton the short-tempered</l>
<l>Protean creator of the Coast Guard</l>
<l>Founder of the New York Post</l>
<l>Ardently abuse his cab’net post</l>
<l>Destroy his reputation?</l>
<l>Welcome, folks, to</l></sp>


<sp who="#burr #company"><speaker>BURR/COMPANY</speaker>
<l>The Adams administration!</l></sp>


<sp who="#burr"><speaker>BURR</speaker>
<l>Jefferson’s the runner-up, which makes him the Vice President</l></sp>


<sp who="#jefferson"><speaker>JEFFERSON</speaker>
<l>Washington can’t help you now, no more mister nice President</l></sp>


<sp who="#burr"><speaker>BURR</speaker>
<l>Adams fires Hamilton</l>
<l>Privately calls him “creole bastard” in his taunts</l></sp>


<sp who="#jefferson"><speaker>JEFFERSON</speaker>
<l>Say what?!</l></sp>


<sp who="#burr"><speaker>BURR</speaker>
<l>Hamilton publishes his response</l></sp>


<sp who="#hamilton"><speaker>HAMILTON</speaker>
<l>Sit down, John, you fat mother—<stage type="delivery">BLEEP</stage></l></sp>


<sp who="#burr"><speaker>BURR</speaker>
<l>Hamilton is out of control</l></sp>


<sp who="#madison"><speaker>MADISON</speaker>
<l>This is great! He’s out of power. He holds no office. And he just destroyed President John Adams, the only other significant member of his party</l></sp>


<sp who="#jefferson"><speaker>JEFFERSON</speaker>
<l>Hamilton’s a host unto himself. As long as he can hold a pen, he’s a threat. Let’s let him know what we know</l></sp>
</div>
